I"À<p>After adding current listened track into my commit message, now iâ€™m adding the action, i take picture everytime commiting something. hereâ€™s how.</p>

<ul>
  <li>get ImageSnap
 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">brew install imagesnap</code> or <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">port install imagesnap</code></li>
  <li>create this hook at your project .git/hooks/</li>
</ul>

<p>the hook</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>#!/bin/bash
COMMITID=$(git rev-parse HEAD)
imagesnap -q -w 1 .gitsnap/$COMMITID.jpg`
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>save as post-commit (so it will run after commit)</p>
